M|traction-eos|This skill is based on the Entrepreneurial Operating System developed by Gino Wickman. For the complete system:
M|traction-eos|- [*"Traction: Get a Grip on Your Business"*](https://www.amazon.com/Traction-Get-Grip-Your-Business/dp/1936661837?tag=wondelai00-20) by Gino Wickman
M|traction-eos|- [*"Get a Grip"*](https://www.amazon.com/Get-Grip-Entrepreneurial-Fable-Business/dp/1939529824?tag=wondelai00-20) by Gino Wickman & Mike Paton (EOS as a business fable)
M|traction-eos|- [*"Rocket Fuel"*](https://www.amazon.com/Rocket-Fuel-Essential-Combination-Business/dp/1941631150?tag=wondelai00-20) by Gino Wickman & Mark C. Winters (Visionary + Integrator relationship)
M|traction-eos|**Gino Wickman** is the creator of EOS (Entrepreneurial Operating System) and founder of EOS Worldwide, a community of certified EOS Implementers who help companies implement the system. Wickman has w